Maximize Win Rate Model Template

Use Case: Binary Classification Use Case

Prerequisites:

* At least 400 closed opportunities with Amounts greater than 0.
* Opportunity Line Items and Activities must be accessible.

Field access: The logged-in user has access to all the fields needed to build an app from the template.
Salesforce configuration: Org uses Record Types.
Data: 400 closed opportunities within the past three years (up to 1095 days).

Generated Assets:

* Model: Maximize Win Rate
* CRM Analytics Dataset: Opportunity Win Rate Training Dataset
* Data Prep Recipe: appName_recipe
* Dashboard: About This Story
* Prediction Definition, Model: Predicted Likelihood to Win, IsWon

Model Outcome Variable and Derived Variables:

* Won (outcome): text
* # Amount Decreased: numeric
* # Amount Increased: numeric
* # Closed Date Pushed: numeric
* # Completed Activities: numeric
* # Lost Opportunities on Account: numeric
* # Won Opportunities on Account: numeric
* Account Tenure: numeric
* Top Product Family: text
* Top Product Name: text

* Create a Model from a Template
